name: Skull of the Cursed Dead’s
description: Another original sculpture created and named by my 10 year old son. This Deadpool/Dead Shot inspired mask was made completely out of duct tape. All proceeds from this OBJKT will get sent to my inactive Airgap wallet which he will receive the seed phrase for when he turns 16. He shows tons of interest and enthusiasm watching me scroll the marketplace and I’m excited to see what his future in the cryptoverse will bloom into!
